column5: ~~~this weekend is Family Day, and to give my family a break I'm going phishen, but where. May be up to the Halliburton area lakes Hmmmm 2 hr drive, maybe back to Lake Stucco, Hmmmm been there, how about renting a hut on Simcoe $$$$ there's always Rice only 40 min.  I'll have to get back to you all
Been curious about Stucco for a while now. Please report back on your decision.
Rice in the winter time? Is it any good?

~~~Not really, off Bewdley about 300Yds most guys are set up, over at Serpent Mound there are a few huts, and Golden Beach Resort they have a few huts, checked over at Gore Landing looks good but nobody there
